Igihe nari mfite imyaka itanu, marume yampaye impano nziza. Cyari icyana cy'ibyumweru bitatu! Umunsi marume yazanye ikibwana murugo, narishimye cyane. Nari nzi ko mfite inshuti.

Nyuma yo kumushira hasi, marume yarahindukiye arambaza ati: "Uzamuha irihe zina?" Narebye icyana cyanjye, ndavuga nti: "Coco." Nyirarume yaratangaye. Abaza ati: "Kuki umwita Coco?" Navuze nti: "Kuberako asa na kakao."

Nabajije marume niba Coco yavutse wenyine. Datawacu yavuze ko hari ikindi kibwana, kimwe na Coco. Nagiye kureba murumuna wa Coco.

Coco abonye murumuna we, arishima cyane. Bombi bashyize imitwe hamwe nkaho bavugana.

Nabajije marume niba nshobora kugumana Coco na murumuna we. Ati: "Ni byiza." "Ariko ugomba kubitaho." Buri mugoroba rero, nakinaga nabo nkabajyana gukora siporo.
Nyuma y'amezi make, Coco na murumuna we bari bakuru, bakomeye kandi bafite ubuzima bwiza. Byari binini cyane ku buryo ntashobora kubireba wenyine.

Nasabye rero marume gusubiza murumuna wa Coco. Ariko igihe Coco yasigara wenyine, yasaga nkababaye cyane. Numvaga ari nk'aho ambaza ati: "Kuki wabikoze?"

Yahagaritse gukina. Rimwe na rimwe yangaga kujyana nanjye. Hari igihe Coco yariye bike cyane. Nari mpangayitse. Nibajije nti: "Niki Nakora kugirango mfashe Coco?"

Umunsi umwe, marume yaje gusura. Numvise ijwi rye, nsohotse mva mu rugo. Mbere yuko mubona, numvise gutontoma kw'imbwa.

Inyuma yigikoni, kubyina bishimye imbere yanjye hari Coco na murumuna we!

Nashimishijwe cyane nuko ntazi uwo guhobera mbere, Coco cyangwa marume. Nari nzi ko Coco azasubira mubuzima bwe bwa kera none murumuna we yagarutse. Twakongera kwiruka mumirima!
